class ListNode:

    def __init__(self, val=0, next=None):
        self.val = val
        self.next = next

def sortLinkedList(head):
    prev = None
    current = head
    while current:
        next_node = current.next
        current.next = prev
        prev = current
        current = next_node
    head = prev
    i = head
    while i or i.next:
        j = i
        while j.next:
            if i.val < j.next.val:
                i_val = i.val
                i.val = j.next.val
                j.next.val = i_val
            j = j.next
        i = i.next
    return head
